description: Variation Of Planning Application 02/2759/FUL Granted Permission On 22.06.04 To Comprise a) Development Of The Existing South Stand To Provide A New Spectator Stand, RFU Store, Ticket Sales Facilities, Hotel, Health And Fitness Club Multi-Functional Conference, Banqueting And Corporate Hospitality Facilites, New RFU Offices And Designated Car Parking In West Car Park And New Vehicular Access To Serve Hotel From Rugby Road. b) Erection Of 2 Blocks Comprising 24 Residential Units With New Access on to Rugby Road. c) Associated Development Including Modifications To Existing Vehicular And Pedestrian Accesses And Provision Of A New Security Gate, Ticket Gates and Perimeter Fencing.
